author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-Re9QQHnBzA1D-k6ABbDqAg">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-Lr-5zb0CPZe0aVTWyeZ61A">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/V%C4%A9nh-ng%E1%BB%99-l%E1%BA%A1c-Nguy%C3%AAn-ti%C3%AAu/poem-bkfnrXBtSep8-ZPjZ1hzPQ">Vĩnh ngộ lạc - Nguyên tiêu - 永遇樂－元宵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-VII/poem-A7W8CNcxY-D9KgCQvQEfBw">Vô đề (VII) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
